data.description:
*** Price Reduction***
THIS 5 BEDROOM & 3.5 BATHROOM HOME IS 2,882 SQFT. Beautiful park views directly across the street, spacious 1st floor with upgraded tile, Gourmet kitchen with double ovens and Master suite conveniently located downstairs. Resort style backyard with pool equipped with water features, LED color change lighting and shaded pergola. Large 2nd floor with spacious loft and walk in closets in each bedroom. Two second story full bathrooms with one conveniently being a Jack and Jill. Upgraded wood look tile in 1st floor powder room and Master bath. Several decorative upgrades throughout home. PROPERTY SCREAMS PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP. Great location with great schools walking distance away in beautiful Verrado neighborhood. Motivated sellers.
